Package: nmrunner
Title: Start NONMEM runs via R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
URL: https://github.com/Clinical-Pharmacy-Saarland-University/nmrunner
BugReports: https://github.com/Clinical-Pharmacy-Saarland-University/nmrunner/issues
Authors@R: 
    person("Dominik", "Selzer", , "dominik.selzer@uni-saarland.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: `nmrunner` facilitates the initiation of NONMEM runs directly from R and subsequently retrieves the results. Designed for compatibility with both Windows and Linux, it offers a suite of auxiliary functions tailored for integration into APIs or interactive platforms like Shiny apps. Emphasizing simplicity, the package is intentionally minimalistic.
